    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a level of preservation that will satisfy the most discerning collector. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior upholstery, demonstrates an uncompromising commitment to care. Mechanical integrity is absolute, ensuring a driving experience that mirrors its original factory delivery. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
